---
title: Chipotle Beef, Charred Corn and Pepper Bowl with Zesty Couscous and Cheese
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Chipotle Beef, Charred Corn and Pepper Bowl in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/14-844e27c7.jpg
